Build and run instructions
==========================

- A computer with unix is needed
- xmllint has to be installed

Build
=====
`make build` to install used python3 packages and download morphodita files

Usage
=====
`./run -q topics-train_cs.xml -d documents_cs.lst -r run-0_cs -o run-0_train_cs.res -document_path documents_cs`

Note arguments `document_path`, which is the path to the folder containing document files.


